          "passage": "Researchers recently found that disruptions to an enjoyable experience, like a shor t series of adver tisements during a television show, often\nincrease viewers’reported enjoyment. Suspecting that disruptions to an unpleasant experience would have the opposite effect, the researchers\nhad participants listen to construction noise for 30 minutes and anticipated that those whose listening experience was frequently interrupted\nwith shor t breaks of silence would thus ______",
