            "guideWrongBreakdown": "How to Solve It: Find the cause-and-effect or contrast in the passage, then pick the answer that follows without needing outside knowledge.\n\nCommon Trap: Adding outside assumptions instead of using only the stated clues.\n\nFinal Takeaway: Stay locked on the exact task: main idea, inference, or evidence support.",
